{"type":"question","id":9908,"title":"我可以在谈笑风生区转载“微信上的翻车新闻”吗？","uid":6760,"topics":[10,722,1957],"contents":"是这样的，我最近关注了一批比较特别的反黑自由派公众号，而这些公众号背后我猜应该是同一拨人在管理的。与其它公众号不同的是，他们总会在文头、文尾配上一些类似翻车新闻的图，而且力度可以说不比翻车新闻小。<br>\n<br>\n这些图片来源于他们的微信读者群。<br>\n<br>\n我就想着能不能转载过来？能不能在标题打上“【微信翻车新闻】第x期”然后打上“【翻车新闻】”的标签？<br>\n<br>\n这是其中几个图。<br>\n-------------------------------------<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/HzvBTwb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HzvBTwb.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/HzvBTwb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xJfq709.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xJfq709.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xJfq709.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EelhZCw.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EelhZCw.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EelhZCw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/16Lw3Qd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/16Lw3Qd.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/16Lw3Qd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NpF8M3V.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NpF8M3V.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NpF8M3V.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/DQZhcCg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DQZhcCg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/DQZhcCg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2wvqY4N.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2wvqY4N.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2wvqY4N.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-13","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}